{"tid":1306213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Memo 紙，撕咗可以再貼","createTime":"2019-07-11T05:29:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T05:39:07.000Z","uid":34705,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"165bbf5e482f1ed06ec2eaffda4c23560399cfc3","tid":1306213,"uid":34705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:29:48.000Z","msg":"仲記唔記得 be water? 廢老又好，撕紙狗又好，佢哋再努力去撕都淨係得一個後果，就係轉頭有更多。希望各位唔好為幅牆令自己受傷，因為只要有心，幅牆喺邊度、任何時候都可以重生，加油！<br />\n<br />\n另外都想同對守住幅牆持反對意見嘅巴絲講聲，我哋應該尊重每個參與者嘅各種抗爭方法，冇話邊個搶咗邊個嘅資源或者 focus，當件事係多人贊同就自然會有人一齊做，記住，唔須要政棍去帶領，因為我哋知道自己需要啲乜，兄弟爬山，各自努力！"},{"pid":"f4037f923714bc4caa04f3cbebed3476aa9d6cba","tid":1306213,"uid":263464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:39:07.000Z","msg":"【任務欄】<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1306215\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1306215</a><br />\n任務眾多，請自行因應人數及背後目的考慮做邊D任 ；<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃色為主線任務</span>；<span style=\"color: red;\">紅色係Boss </span><br />\n7.11 - 梁烈士公眾告別禮 - <a href=\"http://t.me/leung711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fleung711&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt8525R%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=b5702723\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/leung711</a><br />\n7.11 - 油尖旺區議會夢遊 - <a href=\"http://t.me/ytm_dc711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fytm_dc711&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt8525R%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=75489c22\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/ytm_dc711</a><br />\n7.12 - <span style=\"color: gold;\">6.12一周月行動</span> - <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hklsd/photos/a.101378395784/10156221199385785/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhklsd%2Fphotos%2Fa.101378395784%2F10156221199385785%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt8525R%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=f46251b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hklsd/photos/a.101378395784/10156221199385785/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n7.13 - 全民中銀撳錢 - <a href=\"https://t.me/loveBOC\" data-sr-